fin: fin (Command line personal finances manager)
fin:
fin: Keeping track of personal finances is an incredibly boring task, and if
fin: you don't have much money then juggling it can be tricky. When looking at
fin: the existing software out there to manage accounts it's frequently highly
fin: complex and top heavy. Fin - an abbreviation of "financials" - is an
fin: attempt to do the opposite of what most accounting software does, and
fin: that's to make things incredibly simple and quick. Logging a transaction
fin: or viewing your current balance should take no more than a few sec
fin:
